                metabolicIntegration:     "Justify why gluconeogenesis cannot simply be glycolysis running in reverse. Identify the thermodynamic reason that three glycolytic steps are irreversible and explain how bypass enzymes solve this problem.",
                energyAccounting:         "Explain why the modern estimate of ~30 ATP per glucose is lower than the older value of 36–38 ATP. Name two sources of energy 'loss' that the older calculation ignored."
