            verbs: ["Identify", "Determine", "Deduce", "Analyse", "Classify", "Distinguish", "Interpret"],
            whatDistinguishesThisLevel: "Analyze requires the student to move from evidence to conclusion, not from a rule to an answer. Given O₂ consumption data with and without an inhibitor, the student must identify which complex is blocked and explain all downstream consequences — this is analytical, not procedural.",
